7. US Treasury Secretary Bessant: The sovereign wealth fund plan has been suspended;
8. James Wynn cut his ETH and SUI long positions and continued to increase his BTC long positions;
9. US stocks closed: the three major stock indexes all closed lower, and US Steel rose more than 21%;
10. Polygon co-founder Mihailo Bjelic Resigned, becoming the third co-founder to leave;
11. The SEC is reviewing the proposal to list and trade Nasdaq Bitcoin Index options;
12. The US dollar fell to its lowest level since December 2023;
13. Most of the Trump Meme Coin Dinner attendees have transferred or sold their TRUMP coins.
